      "test": "Generate isogenic EPAS1-high vs EPAS1-low ccRCC lines, knock down TOP2A, and assay proliferation, transwell invasion, and in vivo lung colonization; hypothesis fails if TOP2A knockdown does not preferentially impair the EPAS1-low context."
