      "test": "Apply published ClearCode34 logistic model to TCGA-KIRC RNA-seq (normalized FPKM). Compute TOP2A − EPAS1 per sample. Perform Mann-Whitney U test and ROC analysis of the scalar against binary ccA/ccB label. If AUROC < 0.75 or p > 0.001, the ccA/ccB mechanistic framing is falsified."
